TITLE: Creating a Bookmark for Internal Hyperlinks in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a bookmark that will serve as a destination for internal hyperlinks in a document. The bookmark is added to a heading paragraph with an anchor ID and display text.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/hyperlinks.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const chapter1 = new Paragraph({
    heading: HeadingLevel.HEADING_1,
    children: [
        new Bookmark({
            id: "anchorForChapter1",
            children: [new TextRun("Chapter 1")],
        }),
    ],
});
```

