TITLE: Creating a Simple Table in TypeScript using docx
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a basic table and add it to a document section using the docx library. It shows the structure of creating a table with rows and adding it to a document.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/tables.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const table = new Table({
    rows: [Array of `TableRow`s]
});
```

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const doc = new Document({
    sections: [{
        children: [table],
    }],
});
```

