TITLE: Creating an Internal Hyperlink in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to create an internal hyperlink that references a bookmark within the document. The hyperlink includes styled text and points to a specific anchor ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/hyperlinks.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const link = new InternalHyperlink({
    children: [
        new TextRun({
            text: "See Chapter 1",
            style: "Hyperlink",
        }),
    ],
    anchor: "anchorForChapter1",
});
```

