TITLE: Creating Paragraphs using Children Method in DocX (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Creating a paragraph by adding multiple child elements like TextRun and SymbolRun. This method is useful for combining different text styles or adding symbols within a single paragraph.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/paragraph.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
