TITLE: Adding Page References to Bookmarks in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a page reference to a bookmark, which displays the page number where the bookmark is located. It combines regular text with a dynamic page reference.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/hyperlinks.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
