TITLE: Applying Bullet Points to a Paragraph in docx in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to apply the previously defined bullet point formatting to a paragraph. This uses the reference name and level number to link the paragraph to the bullet point style.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/numbering.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

