TITLE: Creating Numbered Item References in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to create cross-references to numbered items in a document. It requires specifying the anchor ID and a cached value for the numbering format.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dolanmiu/docx/blob/master/docs/usage/hyperlinks.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const paragraph = new Paragraph({
    children: [new TextRun("See Paragraph "), new NumberedItemReference("anchorForParagraph1", "1.1")],
});
```

